  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large pan, stir-fry the onion, bell pepper, and tomato until softened.",
    "2. Add the ackee to the pan and stir well.",
    "3. Add the fermented soy sauce and adventurous spices to the pan and stir-fry for 2 minutes.",
    "4. Meanwhile, toast the fry's bread in a toaster or under the broiler.",
    "5. Assemble the dish by placing the toasted bread on a plate, topping it with the ackee mixture, and drizzling with juicy juice.",
    "6. Serve hot and enjoy!"
